data.description: Assumable loan at 3.25%! Discover Your Dream Home in Round Rock, Texas! Welcome to 2106 Bluebonnet, a spacious 3 bed, 2 bath, 2-story gem in the coveted Chandler Creek neighborhood. With plenty of square footage, this home offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and efficiency. The kitchen seamlessly opens to the dining room and a generously sized living room, making it an entertainer's delight. What sets this property apart is its versatile converted garage, ready to be your home gym, studio, game room, or even a cozy home theater. The primary bedroom and bath are conveniently located downstairs, while upstairs boasts an open loft and two additional bedrooms. Outside, a spacious lot with large shade trees provides a serene oasis, and the backyard shed is ready to house your treasures. Recent updates abound, including fresh paint, a roof with a 30-year warranty, energy-efficient solar panels, triple-pane windows, and stylish fixtures throughout. The included solar panel system means potential savings and energy independence, and it's open to negotiation if you'd prefer a lower sales price. Imagine not worrying about power bills and enjoying stability in any Texas grid situation. What's more, the house enjoys excellent sun exposure and is conveniently located near a well-maintained HOA park with numerous amenities, and all your daily needs are within a mile's reach. This property is a rare find – don't miss the opportunity to make it your own! Contact us today for more details and to schedule a viewing.
